caption: Tried the hot Vanilla Chai - it was very good!  Nice courteous service.

So I’m in Brooklyn for the weekend and I’ve eaten here three times because it’s that good. The customer service is amazing everyone is friendly and laughing. I had a egg cheese pastrami on a bagel it’s to die for. They also have Kim Bucher
Holy Cuban Sandwich! It was probably the best I ever ate. They don't press the sandwich which is IMO way better. So good.
Best quality food,  fesh ingredient.   I love this food
Absolutely love the food, coffee and service. It’s everything you want in your local coffee shop, consistently.
Delicious, fast, and wonderful, friendly staff.
All the sandwiches are awesome. The coffee and sweet treats too! Tuna melt is my go-to!
Friendly staff, fast service, quality food
Very good
Turkey clubs are amazing and their iced latte is to die for. Love love love this place
Oh my gosh the best Brooklyn coffee shop I’ve ever been to. I love the energy super friendly staff. I love that they have different flavors of kombucha. Thank you again for your service 🙏🏽

I Recently moved into this neighborhood and came across this awesome place .  I come here often and I usually ride bike here , the staff is so friendly they even wrap up my ice coffee so it won't spill!! I mean can I say outstanding customer service. The staff is nice and super fast !  I call in my order for most part and I've tried literally every sandwich and never been disappointed!  This place has been open through out the pandemic and I wanted thank them for feeding me and providing me and roommates with coffee . You guys are the best🥇
Not a fan of this spot anymore. Rude af
Coffee is amazing, particularly their lattes. Their food also never disappoints! Plus, they always arrive super fast.
So glad I found this spot during the pandemic. This is the sandwich to brighten up anyone’s day. The staff are kind and made great recommendations. Thank you!

If you love delicious sandwiches this is is absolutely without a doubt the best place to come too.  I always get the chiplote chicken on a plain bagel that's my go to sandwich. And my other favorite is the steak egg and cheese on plain bagel.  Service and food is on another level ... staff is awesome you guys rock  cheers to Brooklyn Baristas . ❤️❤️❤️❤️
Best BLT. Bangin' coffee. Dope bread options. Down-to-Earth staff. And inexpensive for 1) NY standards and 2) the portion size. This place is straight up addictive!

This sandwich shop has such a great variation,  the sandwiches are extremely tasty, prepared with high quality , huge and most importantly made with love!  I've been coming here since they opened and staff is really accommodating and friendly .  FYI I've tried everything on menu and it's awesome!  I love you Brooklyn Barista ❤️

This place is the perfect place to get a bite to eat and a wonderful cup of coffee among other things. They make great sandwiches and the vibe is relaxing and refreshing. Stop in and try for yourself. You won't be disappointed.they also have a decent selection of juice and health drinks. Enjoy! My 4th time in here and the food and beverage is consistently wonderful. I would definitely come here daily if possible. The vibe is great and the service is outstanding. If Brooklyn Barista was a woman, I would marry her in a heartbeat. I really love this place. Stop in and fall in love with the wonderful atmosphere and perfectly prepared food and beverages. I can't wait to get back and enjoy everything that Brooklyn Barista is!

The coffee is really good here. They have bagels and a few choices in various types of cream cheese. There are pastries and a few choices in other food. I will definitely be going back. If you drive, I suggest parking on the side streets close to the shop. There's no parking on the main road near the shop. There is indoor seating.
Good food, and even better coffee! What really made me fall for this place was how genuinely friendly they were, this is going to become a regular spot for me!

Best sandwich shop in town !  I order a lot here during my lunch hour , I then ordered for catering - can I say awesome job!!!! Sandwiches were all nicely stacked and perfect ...  This is absolutely one of my favorite places
A+ Classic NY bagel shop, with excellent customer service and delicious food. As an added bonus, they make your food very, very quickly.
Just had coffee and a bagel from there. Love this place. Feels very family owned.
Best coffee shop I’ve ever been to! Coffee taste great and their sandwich menu is to die for. Amazing, friendly and professional staff. Wish I can come here everyday!

I come here a few times a week I’m guilty of even coming everyday...  They have delicious sandwiches and they do it well !!!  Staff is very friendly and super attentive. For instance last Sunday I was here with 8 of my friends , and all of our orders was correctly labeled and it was already packed - prior to our arrival.  All in all, awesome job to the staff I know it’s not easy being In the food service industry & dealing with people..  My favorite spot!
Yummy coffee and great breakfast sandwiches

I love this place this sandwich shop so much, food is incredible and I get my coffee every morning here prior to going to work!  When my family comes over this is my show off spot,  because it's great customer service......       I appreciate  the staff they know my name and outstanding customer service ...  more importantly the food is amazing along with the coffee.

I come here couple times a week during my lunch hour, and I must admit I’m One loyal customer.  Let’s begin with what’s most important to Me, “the Food” their sandwiches are just very savory, mouth watering consistency deliciousness!!!!!  One of my top favorite is the Italian sub along with the tuna melt on an everything bagel.  I’m able to get two important factors to get me through my day which is coffee and super delicious sandwich....
They have vegan treats, but im not happy about the wifi 2 hr time limit.
Awesome sandwiches, great caffeine options and super friend staff.

Good breakfast sandwich, cappuccino, and vegan doughnut at reasonable prices. Nice staff and atmosphere as well.  Definitely hot in there on a summer day but seemed the AC was getting set up. Will definitely come again to try other food.
Great coffee friendly staff

Deliciousness , consistency very nice staff!!! What else can you ask for???  I come here everyday before work and for lunch hour. The sandwiches are delicious every time it's just to perfection!!! The staff super friendly at all times... if I'm in a rush I try call in my order prior to getting there ....  I try come on weekend with my mom she loves the

Great coffee shop, cozy and well decorated. Nice to do some work while having some great coffee. They also have a sandwiches menu, which are pretty good (at leas the ones I had). The baristas are also super friendly :)
Spicy Turkey sandwich was very good
Excellent...💪💪
I love stuff who’s working there, their espresso just perfect! Bagels are delicious as well 🖤🖤🖤

I love this place. Great coffee and great Sandwiches paired with awesome customer service. I go here maybe 3-4 times a week and I usually order 4 Bacon egg and cheese for my friends to. The sandwhiches here are the best and it's really nice that they dont get upset because I'm ordering 4 sandwhiches at once. Not to mention the sandwhiches are good AF and they make everything really fast.
This place is really awesome and comfy. Oh yeah, great food and beverages as well 😉  Greetings from 🇩🇪✌️😎
Very friendly people
Nicely decorated and cozy neighborhood coffee shop. They have great strong coffee and friendly staff. I love the lox combo on the bagel, delicious!
Great selection of coffees and chill drink and stream the web on their wifi

This has to be one of my favorite spots in Bushwick I come out of my way to get their delicious bagels along with my usual cappuccino with oat milk.  I come here every Saturday and Sunday with my best friends this is the go to!  Friendly staff delicious coffee and food and pastries.  I recommend pastrami egg and cheddar and vegan brownies OMG! Delicious  Rock on Brooklyn Barista!
Best coffee in the area and bagels are great as well. The nice staff is what makes this place special!
Great place to chill
Amazing place for coffee, WiFi and getting some work done. And the sandwiches are excellent

Great coffee, really good bagels and even better vegan brownies! Lots of food and drinks choices - great for a quick coffee or for spending a while working on your laptop over a sweet treat and coffee. Staff are really lovely too! Brilliant little coffee shop

Great spot with friendly staff.
What I like most about this place is the service they give and the staff are very friendly!

Nice little coffee shop/deli. They had super delicious vegan brownies and all the alt milks you could want (go for Oatly, you won't be disappointed)! The woman at the counter was super nice! Good quiet place for working too, they have outlets and WiFi and it's not crowded.
Great small coffee shop. Perfect place to meet someone. Cute decorations and moderately priced.
My new favorite coffee bar in the area!

I’ve been couple times but my roommate comes for a coffee everyday, he and I are impressed with their service because it’s always on point since they opened. There’s a lot of natural light, nice decoration, a nice sandwich menu and super clean. Their staff is super friendly and accommodating. There’s no doubt this is the best coffee shop in the neighborhood
The best coffeeshop in town! It has nice coffee and yummy bagels. Also has a hip atmosphere!

(Translated by Google) Very good address, the coffee, drinks, pastries and bagels are excellent. The reception is always at the top!  (Original) Très bonne adresse, le café, les boissons, les pâtisseries et les bagels sont excellents. L'accueil est toujours au top!

Growing up in Brooklyn i always wished we had a good coffee shop, finally god heard my prayers , this is by far one of the best Coffee shop i been to.  They have the best Sandwiches i ever had. I love the customer services . Highly Recommend !!!!!!!

The best coffee shop I been to thus far! The sandwiches are all delicious (so hard to choose one) the coffee is just brewed freshly to perfection and to top it off not only is the place beautiful and cozy but also the staff are so friendly and welcoming! Wishing the owners of Brooklyn Barista much success!
Great place to sit with a coffee

Just moved into the neighborhood and I’m in love with this coffee shop.  I get my perfect combination of a great cup coffee along with my breakfast. I’m able to eat it here and go right before I start my day.  Fast service, super friendly staff and cute and cozy location!  Rock on Brooklyn Barista!!

It's fine. You can tell a lot of the clientele comes from that new, fancy apartment complex right across the street, sitting there in their "thrift store" clothes writing poetry and whatnot, but that isn't this place's fault. Personally, I find the espresso/lattes aren't quite as good as trans am right down the street, but there is more seating here, so that's a plus.

A wonderful cafe with very welcoming staff. They serve a good, strong cup of Toby's Estate drip. The blueberry crumb muffin was top-notch. This neighborhood is in the midst of change. I'm visiting my daughter (3 years since last time) and am surprised by the new construction, restaurants, and, of course, breweries. I assume many locals don't like this, but change is inevitable and often advantageous (e.g., new jobs). I lived in Oakland 20 years and witnessed blight become bright. Wishing Brooklyn Barista continued success!

First - they have so many Kombucha varieties which is one of my favorite things.  I’m able get my coffee, breakfast and kombucha all in one location.  Would this describe this coffee shop as Clean , cute and cozy. Looking forward to trying every sandwich on that menu!
